ISLAMABAD, Oct 30 (APP): President Dr Arif Alvi Sunday expressed grief and sorrow over the demise of television journalist Sadaf Naeem.
In a message, he prayed to Allah Almighty to rest the departed soul in eternal peace and grant courage to the bereaved family to bear the loss with fortitude.
